This project has a graphify knowledge graph at `graphify-out/` (corpus: **`src/` only**, see `.graphifyignore`).

## Cursor agent workflow

- Run commands from the **repository root** using **`.venv/bin/graphify`** (not bare `graphify` — CLI lives in the project venv).
- For questions about `src/` architecture, symbols, or call flow: when `graphify-out/graph.json` exists, run:
  - `.venv/bin/graphify query "<question>"`
  - `.venv/bin/graphify path "<A>" "<B>"` or `.venv/bin/graphify explain "<concept>"`
- Prefer query results over grepping `src/` or opening many files.
- Read `graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md` only for broad architecture review.
- After editing files under `src/` in this session: `.venv/bin/graphify update .` (AST-only, no API cost).
- For full `/graphify` rebuild flags and edge cases, follow `.cursor/skills/graphify/SKILL.md`.

## Out of scope

Do not expect graph coverage for `uspi/`, `docs/`, or repo-root build files — only `src/` is indexed.
